{{ 'kt-product-variant-picker.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}
{%- comment -%}
  R166 SHOWROOM-BUY-PARITY-1: the buy_controls block now renders the
  canonical snippets/product-form.liquid. Its styles live in
  kt-product-form.css (shared with main-product.liquid). Loading
  unconditionally is safe — file is small and the block is part of
